<p>Rob started out as part of KUWTK but then drew back from the series as he battled weight gain and health issues.</p>

<p>He returned to the limelight with his own spin-off Rob &amp; Chyna in 2016 which followed him and then-fiancee Blac Chyna in the run-up to the birth of their daughter Dream.</p>

<p>The couple split for good in early 2017 and Rob once again dropped out of the spotlight.</p>

